	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To sort tiles to be usable to you, I reccomand opening a new file, and put all tiles there in the order you want. Once you finished modified them, do the opposite to put them back in the ROM.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


