		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Another quick question.
<br />
<br />Are mappers used to access the CHR-RAM.  Kind of like switching to different levels (e.g. when you play Zelda and walking through the map and then go into a house or sumptin where you talk to someone).  RIght?

		

